**hibernate.cfg.xml**:

    &lt;property name=&quot;dialect&quot;&gt;org.hibernate.dialect.MySQL5Dialect&lt;/property&gt;

Only Change done is:

    &lt;property name=&quot;dialect&quot;&gt;org.hibernate.dialect.MySQL5Dialect&lt;/property&gt;

from

    &lt;property name=&quot;dialect&quot;&gt;org.hibernate.dialect.MySQLDialect&lt;/property&gt;

